snippet.title: Baap Ka Biyaah - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Papaji hain lonely aur Amit hai unka only son.Beta jawaan ho gaya hai but papa wants a companion for life. Dosari taraf Amit ki girlfriend bhi hona chahati hai uski wife.Is sabke beech phansi hui hai Amit ki jaan; aur tabhi life mein aa jati hai Miss Santosh jo hai Papa ki bhooli bisri girlfriend aur abhi tak hai single jiske sath Papa karna chahate hain mingle. Kya dad ko milegi unki dulhaniya? Kya Papa ke sath Amit ka ghar bhi basega ya vo kisi aur chakkar mein phansega? Is parivarik comedy mein mil jayenge saare jawaab. To baap ke biha mein jalool jalool aana aur like, share, comment karke jana.

snippet.title: Angaar (Official Video) - IKKA Ft. Raftaar | Sez On The Beat | Mass Appeal India | New song 2020
snippet.description:
IKKA and Raftaar reunite after 10 years on “Angaar” with music produced by one of India’s premier producers Sez On The Beat of Gully Boy fame. “Angaar,” literally translated to mean ‘Fire,’ narrates the collective experiences of both artists within hip hop and society.

➟  Download & Stream IKKA’s debut hip hop album “I”: https://ikka.lnk.to/ialbum 
#IKKA #Raftaar #AngaarHai #I

IKKA’s debut album “I” is out now and features collaborations with desi hip hop’s most elite and prolific rappers and music producers like Raftaar, DIVINE, Lil Golu, Sikander Kahlon, Sez On The Beat, Phenom, Byg Byrd, DJ MissyK, Hardbazy and Ashock. 

“I” showcases IKKA’s deep-routed experiences and brotherhood within the hip hop community (Angaar and Level Up), his lifestyle (Aajkal and Maujjan), his attitude (Khatma and Gaanewale Rapper), his alter ego as a gamer (PS4 Pro), and his societal reflections (Conversation and Demon). 

♫ Spotify: https ://ikka.lnk.to/ialbum/spotify 

♫ Gaana: https ://ikka.lnk.to/ialbum/gaana  

♫ Apple Music : https://ikka.lnk.to/ialbum/applemusic

snippet.title: TOM & JERRY - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Tom and Jerry take their cat-and-mouse game to the big screen. Watch the trailer for the new #TomAndJerryMovie now – coming to theaters 2021.

One of the most beloved rivalries in history is reignited when Jerry moves into New York City’s finest hotel on the eve of “the wedding of the century,” forcing the event’s desperate planner to hire Tom to get rid of him, in director Tim Story’s “Tom & Jerry.”  The ensuing cat and mouse battle threatens to destroy her career, the wedding and possibly the hotel itself. But soon, an even bigger problem arises: a diabolically ambitious staffer conspiring against all three of them. 

An eye-popping blend of classic animation and live action, Tom and Jerry’s new big-screen adventure stakes new ground for the iconic characters and forces them to do the unthinkable… work together to save the day.   

 “Tom & Jerry” stars Chloë Grace Moretz (“Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising,” “The Addams Family”), Michael Peña (“Cesar Chavez,” “American Hustle,” “Ant-Man”), Rob Delaney (“Deadpool 2,” “Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw”), Colin Jost (“How to be Single,” “Saturday Night Live”), and Ken Jeong (“Crazy Rich Asians,” “The Hangover,” “Transformers: Dark of the Moon”).  
The film is directed by Tim Story (“Fantastic Four,” “Think Like a Man,” “Barbershop”) and produced by Chris DeFaria (“The LEGO Movie 2,” “Ready Player One,” “Gravity”).  

It is written by Kevin Costello, based on characters created by William Hanna and Joseph Barbera.  Serving as executive producers are Tim Story, Adam Goodman, Steven Harding, Sam Register, Jesse Ehrman, and Allison Abbate. The creative filmmaking team includes director of photography Alan Stewart, production designer James Hambidge, editor Peter S. Elliot, and costume designer Alison McCosh.  The music is composed by Christopher Lennertz.  
A Warner Bros. Pictures and Warner Animation Group presentation, a Tim Story Film, “Tom & Jerry” will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. 

The film is rated PG for cartoon violence, rude humor and brief language.

snippet.title: CHICKEN FRY | Pallipalayam Chicken Recipe Cooking In Village  Tamil Nadu Special Country Chicken Fry
snippet.description:
Today we cook healthy country chicken meat to make the Pallipalayam Chicken Fry recipe. This chicken recipe is very famous across Tamil Nadu. Tamil Nadu has native famous three types of chicken fry recipes which are very authentic and made by villagers.

Chettinad Uppu Kari, Chinthamani Chicken, and Chicken Pallipalayam. Taste is similar from one by other But these are real village chicken fry recipes with the country chicken meat.

In the not too distant future, Todd Hewitt (Tom Holland) discovers Viola (Daisy Ridley), a mysterious girl who crash lands on his planet, where all the women have disappeared and the men are afflicted by “the Noise” – a force that puts all their thoughts on display. In this dangerous landscape, Viola’s life is threatened – and as Todd vows to protect her, he will have to discover his own inner power and unlock the planet’s dark secrets.

From the director of The Bourne Identity and Edge of Tomorrow and based on the best-selling novel The Knife of Never Letting Go, Daisy Ridley and Tom Holland star with Mads Mikkelsen, Demián Bichir, Cynthia Erivo, Nick Jonas, Kurt Sutter, and David Oyelowo in Chaos Walking.

snippet.title: Will Smith Tears Up Ending 'Fresh Prince' Feud w/ Janet Hubert
snippet.description:
Will Smith and Janet Hubert have finally put their differences aside! The former co-stars sat down together for the first time in 27 years during "The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air" reunion special on HBO Max to discuss the actress' contentious exit from the sitcom nearly three decades earlier. Hubert originally played Aunt Viv for three seasons of the show. She left in 1993 citing "creative differences" and was replaced by Daphne Maxwell Reid. The casting shakeup sparked an ongoing feud between Smith and Hubert, which has continued in the public eye — until now!

Come thrifting with me in NYC! In this video, I give you a tour of my favorite thrift stores in Manhattan and Brooklyn, try on all the thrifted dresses, jackets, sweaters, jeans, and t-shirts I’ve accumulated over the past couple months, and demonstrate my hidden talent of stuffing a truly obscene amount of fabric into my pants. Also thank you for your patience with my upload schedule during the past month! I tried to film this thrift haul a couple weeks ago on election day and the vibes were just ~weird~ because I was so nervous, so I decided to scrap the entire thing, and then there’s been a ton of construction in my building so it’s been infuriatingly hard to find a time quiet enough to film. Anyhow an entire month later, here she is!

snippet.title: How To Super Clean Cloth and Leather Seats
snippet.description:
Learn how to clean and detail stained cloth and leather seats in your car.  In this video I show you how to clean really dirty cloth seats with mud and stains in them as well as slightly dirty cloth seats which still need to be cleaned! I will also show you how to clean leather seats and use the corect leather cleaner and leather conditioner. The Super Clean series is about attention to detail so not only are we cleaning the interior but we are protecting it.

In the not too distant future, Todd Hewitt (Tom Holland) discovers Viola (Daisy Ridley), a mysterious girl who crash lands on his planet, where all the women have disappeared and the men are afflicted by “the Noise” – a force that puts all their thoughts on display. snippet.title: Will Smith Tears Up Ending 'Fresh Prince' Feud w/ Janet Hubert
snippet.description:
Will Smith and Janet Hubert have finally put their differences aside! The former co-stars sat down together for the first time in 27 years during "The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air" reunion special on HBO Max to discuss the actress' contentious exit from the sitcom nearly three decades earlier. Hubert originally played Aunt Viv for three seasons of the show. She left in 1993 citing "creative differences" and was replaced by Daphne Maxwell Reid. The casting shakeup sparked an ongoing feud between Smith and Hubert, which has continued in the public eye — until now!

snippet.title: Barack Obama: The 2020 60 Minutes interview
snippet.description:
The former president shares the advice he would give President Trump, his thoughts on the killing of George Floyd, and what's behind the divisions in Washington and across the U.S. Scott Pelley reports. https://cbsn.ws/3kyvQRG

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

what if I what if I sin, what if I what if I break

Lifting me up, lifting me up, yeah and tearing me down, tearing me down, down, down,
Take responsibility for everything I’ve done, holding it against me like you’re the holy one
I had a chip on my shoulder, had to let it go
Cause unforgiveness keeps them in control, I came in with good intentions then I let it go
And now I really wanna know
What if I what if I trip, what if I what if I fall, I fall
Then am I the monster, just let me know
what if I what if I sin, what if I what if I break yeah
Then am I the monster, just let me know
Please just let me know

Please don’t let me fall
Oh please don’t let me fall
What if I’m the monster, what if I’m the monster yeah

snippet.title: After Trump Lost Election, See How He's Losing In Court | The Beat With Ari Melber | MSNBC
snippet.description:
In a special report, MSNBC's Chief Legal Correspondent Ari Melber debunks Trump’s voter “fraud” claims with the facts and the judges’ own words from court. Melber highlights the fact that Trump's own lawyer admitted there's no evidence of voter fraud under oath and that Trump's own aides are privately acknowledging they're aware this legal fight is "unsustainable." Aired on 11/12/2020.
» Subscribe to MSNBC: http://on.msnbc.com/SubscribeTomsnbc

"The Beat" features guest interviews in addition to reporting on stories from across the country. The stories that are covered span across the political spectrum. In addition to his law background, Melber is a former Senate staffer, giving him a unique perspective to share on the political happenings coming out of Washington, D.C.

snippet.title: Barack Obama speaks out on politics, life in the White House, and Donald Trump
snippet.description:
In his first television interview since the election of Joe Biden as the 46th President, former President Barack Obama sits down with "CBS This Morning" co-host Gayle King to discuss the first volume of his memoirs, "A Promised Land." He talks about the enormous opposition he experienced as he entered the White House; the impact of his political career on his family; and why he campaigned for his former vice president – and spoke out so vociferously against his successor, President Donald Trump.

snippet.title: Barack Obama: The 2020 60 Minutes interview
snippet.description:
The former president shares the advice he would give President Trump, his thoughts on the killing of George Floyd, and what's behind the divisions in Washington and across the U.S. Scott Pelley reports. https://cbsn.ws/3kyvQRG

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu

Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 — Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this world, consumed by neverending conflict, sometimes only an outsider will get the job done. And that's you.

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC, and Google Stadia on December 10th, 2020. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character’s cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:
https://www.cyberpunk.net 
https://www.twitter.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.facebook.com/CyberpunkGame 
https://www.instagram.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.discord.gg/CyberpunkGame
https://www.CyberpunkGame.tumblr.com

Tracks:

Title: Come Close
Created by: Sebastian Robertson and Daniel Davies

Title: Suicide
Created by: Geno Lenardo feat. Valin "ZEALE" Zamerron

Title: Makes Me Feel Better
Created by: Kevin Hastings

His five-part docuseries ‘The Last Ride’ is currently airing on the WWE Network. On November 22 he'll be giving his "Final Farewell" at ‘Survivor Series,’ the same event where he made his wrestling debut more than 30 years ago. snippet.title: Crew-1 Mission | Launch
snippet.description:
Coast Phase: https://youtu.be/eVB02SSeqgQ

SpaceX and NASA are targeting Sunday, November 15 for Falcon 9’s launch of Dragon’s first operational crew mission (Crew-1) to the International Space Station (ISS) from historic Launch Complex 39A (LC-39A) at NASA’s Kennedy Space Center in Florida. The instantaneous launch window opens at 7:27 p.m. EST on November 15, 00:27 UTC on November 16. Following stage separation, SpaceX will attempt to land Falcon 9’s first stage on the “Just Read the Instructions” droneship, which will be stationed in the Atlantic Ocean. The launch webcast will go live about 4 hours before liftoff. Tune in here to watch live.

localizations.en.description: SpaceX and NASA are targeting Sunday, November 15 for Falcon 9’s launch of Dragon’s first operational crew mission (Crew-1) to the International Space Station (ISS) from historic Launch Complex 39A (LC-39A) at NASA’s Kennedy Space Center in Florida. The instantaneous launch window opens at 7:27 p.m. EST on November 15, 00:27 UTC on November 16. Following stage separation, SpaceX will attempt to land Falcon 9’s first stage on the “Just Read the Instructions” droneship, which will be stationed in the Atlantic Ocean. The launch webcast will go live about 4 hours before liftoff. Tune in here to watch live.

snippet.title: Gabriela Rocha, Kim Walker-Smith – Seu Nome É Amor (Love Has a Name)
snippet.description:
Seu Nome é Amor (Love Has a Name) - Gabriela Rocha + Kim Walker-Smith | Assista minha playlist de músicas: https://onilnk.com/r/SeuNomeEAmor
Inscreva-se no canal Gabriela Rocha: https://onilnk.com/r/GabrielaRocha 

Official vídeo for “Seu Nome é Amor (Love Has a Name)” by Kim Walker-Smith and Gabriela Rocha 
Gravado no início de Março/2020, antes das restrições da pandemia. Recorded in early March/2020 before pandemic restrictions. 
_____
LYRICS (LETRA) Written by (Compositores): Kim Walker-Smith, Ricky Jackson e Ran Jackson

Há um vazio em cada coração 
Há um anseio, que vai além do céu 
Há resposta, pra toda questão 
Há um nome 
Há esperança em meu interior 
Há uma voz que ecoa em meio à dor 
Há uma chama pronta pra queimar
 Há um nome
Fixo meu olhar sobre Aquele que venceu 
Grande é o Senhor 
Que as correntes já rompeu 
Seu nome é amor 
Seu nome é amor, Jesus (bis)
There's a joy that Triumphs over fear 
There's a laughter that Wipes away all tears 
There's a presence That changes atmospheres 
There's a name 
We will fix our eyes 
On the One who overcame 
We will stand in awe 
Of the One who breaks the chains 
Love has a name 
Love has a name, Jesus (bis)
Seu nome é exaltado 
Pra sempre 
Seu nome estremece céus e terra 
A nossa esperança 
O nosso Salvador, Jesus, Jesus 
Seu nome é amor 
Seu nome é amor Jesus 
Seu nome é alegria 
Seu nome é alegria, Jesus 
Victory has a name 
Victory has a name, Jesus 
Love has a name 
Love has a name, Jesus 
 ___ 
Gabriela Rocha nasceu em São Paulo no ano de 1994. Aos 5 anos iniciou seu ministério na igreja que frequentava, quando aos 13 participou do programa Raul Gil, onde suas voz se propagou pela nação. A partir de então, a cantora se dedicou por completo ao chamado do Senhor em se tornar voz de Deus, levando os louvores e ministrações a todos os povos. Em 2012 Gabriela lançou seu primeiro álbum “Jesus”, em 2014 “Pra Onde Iremos?” e em 2016, “EP Gabriela Rocha” e “Até Transbordar (Ao Vivo)”, seu primeiro CD/DVD ao vivo. Seu segundo EP, “Céu”, foi lançado em 2017 e tornou-se repertório das igrejas brasileiras e internacionais. Em 2019 ela lançou o EP “Hosana” com canções como: Eu e o Rei (Ao Vivo), A Ele a Glória (Ao Vivo) e Diz. Em 2020 lançou a canção “Lugar Secreto (Español)”, que contou com a participação de Christine D'Clario, o EP “Juntos Em Adoração (Live 2020)” que chegou junto com a estreia do canal da ministra no PodCast na plataforma e a canção “Teu Espírito”  e “Seu Nome é Amor” que contou com a collab de Kim Walker Smith - gravado no início de Março/2020, antes das restrições da pandemia - (Recorded in early March/2020 before pandemic restrictions). Ouça e seja abençoado(a)!

snippet.title: PlayStation 5: Evento de Lançamento Brasil
snippet.description:
É com grande prazer e empolgação que nós anunciamos nosso evento digital para a chegada da nova geração: Evento de Lançamento do PlayStation 5 no Brasil. Mais que um lançamento, a chegada do PlayStation 5 é um momento digno para celebrar!

Como bons brasileiros, nós teremos uma grande festa com muitas atrações e surpresas. Entre os convidados da livestream estão o Time PlayStation, uma equipe de platina formada por Projota, Bibi Tatto, Gabriel Medina, Fernanda Gentil, Bruno Corrêa e Coisa de Nerd! Eles jogarão com outros convidados, os youtubers gamers que os fãs já conhecem e amam.

Além disso, para tornar o evento ainda mais festivo, teremos um momento Spotify, para promover o nosso novo Controle de Mídia do PlayStation 5 e seu botão dedicado para o aplicativo. A atração será um pocket show do Projota! Também compartilharemos o link de uma playlist especial para o público gamer feita no Spotify. Se juntem a nós para o lançamento do PlayStation 5 no Brasil!



#PS5NoBrasil #PlayHasNoLimits #JogarNaoTemLimites

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 — Trailer Oficial de Gameplay
snippet.description:
Neste mundo consumido por conflitos sem fim, às vezes apenas um forasteiro terminará o serviço. E esse é você.

Cyberpunk 2077, uma história de ação e aventura de mundo aberto da CD PROJEKT RED, está chegando para Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC e Google Stadia em 10 de dezembro de 2020. O título também será jogável nos consoles Xbox Series X e PlayStation 5, quando disponíveis.

Reserve agora: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

Sobre o jogo:
Cyberpunk 2077 é uma história de ação e aventura de mundo aberto ambientada em Night City, uma megalópole obcecada por poder, glamour e biomodificações. Você joga como V, um mercenário fora da lei atrás de um implante único que carrega a chave da imortalidade. Você pode personalizar aparatos cibernéticos, conjunto de habilidades e estilo de jogo do personagem e explorar uma vasta cidade onde as decisões tomadas definem a história e o mundo ao seu redor.

snippet.title: (TRAILER OFICIAL) TEOCRACIA EM VERTIGEM - ESPECIAL DE NATAL
snippet.description:
“Podemos nos tornar um Hindu melhor, um Muçulmano melhor, um Católico melhor." (Madre Teresa de Calcutá) 

“Meu apelo por uma revolução espiritual não é um apelo por uma revolução religiosa.” (Dalai Lama) 

"Separar dele não posso, porque ia escandalizar o nome de Deus." (Flordelis)  

Muitas são as frases que marcaram como a humanidade interpreta a religião através do tempo, mas agora chegou a hora de entender o lado verdadeiro da história. Sem tomar partidos ou cair em ideologias. 

Jesus sofreu golpe? Queriam a hemorroida de Barrabás? Os apóstolos realmente estocaram vento? Só sabemos de uma coisa: o julgamento final chegou, a teocracia está em vertigem e ninguém vai ganhar, vai todo mundo perder! E quem perder vai ganhar perdendo.  

Dia 10 de dezembro NÃO ASSISTA Teocracia em Vertigem, o novo Especial de Natal do Porta dos Fundos aqui no YouTube. 

#EspecialdeNataldoPorta #NãoAssista 

--- O vídeo é uma obra artística de humor e sátira religiosa, que não retrata - necessariamente - de forma fiel a realidade, fatos históricos ou eventos bíblicos. O vídeo foi produzido pela produtora Porta dos Fundos e não se confunde com as convicções e opções religiosas dos seus produtores e atores.

Dia 10 de dezembro NÃO ASSISTA Teocracia em Vertigem, o novo Especial de Natal do Porta dos Fundos aqui no YouTube. 

#EspecialdeNataldoPorta #NãoAssista 

--- O vídeo é uma obra artística de humor e sátira religiosa, que não retrata - necessariamente - de forma fiel a realidade, fatos históricos ou eventos bíblicos. O vídeo foi produzido pela produtora Porta dos Fundos e não se confunde com as convicções e opções religiosas dos seus produtores e atores.

snippet.title: Challenge: Krieg den Wendler ans Handy || Das schaffst du nie!
snippet.description:
2020 war sein Jahr! Mal besser, meistens schlechter: Der Wendler! 

 Etliche Parodien zum Video von Lauras kleinem SUV-Geschenk, sein Battle mitn Oliver Pocher oder ein vermeintlich geleaktes Bild von seinem kleinen Wendler. Aber alles EGAL: Denn nun kriegt er seine eigene Challenge bei DSDN! Meini bekommt die Aufgabe, den Wendler zu erreichen. Telefon, Facetime, Teleram, egal wie! Ob Sebastian Meinberg es schafft, Michael Wendler ans Telefon zu bekommen, seht ihr in der neuen Folge von „Das schaffst du nie!“. 

BAAAABY, ICH LIEBE DICH! 

Für die heutige Challenge bekommt Meini drei Stunden Zeit. Das Ziel ist einfach: Telefoniere mit dem Wendler. Die Wendler Fans unter euch wissen natürlich, dass er in Florida lebt. Daran hat Marc Seibold natürlich gedacht und für die Challenge die Zeitverschiebung schon miteingerechnet. Nicht, dass Meini den Wendler aus seinen süßen Träumen reißt. Nach dem kürzlichen Nummernleak von RTL ist es natürlich umso schwieriger ihn ans Telefon zu kriegen und deshalb eine perfekte Challenge für „Das schaffst du nie!“. 

 

EINE STRAßE, VIELE BÄUME, JA DAS IST EINE ALLEE 

Auf dem Weg zum Wendler versucht unser Moderator Sebastian Meinberg natürlich alles! Manche von euch haben bereits vor einigen Tagen mitbekommen, dass er ein Aufruf auf Instagram gestartet hat. Wir können zumindest schon so viel verraten: Er hat die halbe Schlagerszene durchtelefoniert und einige Überraschungen für euch parat! Richtige Kultfiguren aus dem Bierkönig! Ist das die nötige Wendlung für den Sieg? 

 

#funk #dsdn #dasschaffstdunie 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72h moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei „Das schaffst du nie!“ stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge – gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, dürfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, müssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt’s ein neues Video von „Das schaffst du nie!“. Heute: Ruf nen Star an. Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung. 

Wer Sebastian bei der nächsten Challenge sehen möchte, klickt hier: https://www.instagram.com/heinz.wescher/ 

Und wer Marc folgen möchte, klickt hier: https://instagram.com/marc_cyborg ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

snippet.title: Historische Blamage für chancenlose DFB-Elf: Spanien - Deutschland 6:0 | UEFA Nations League | DAZN
snippet.description:
Die deutsche Nationalmannschaft kassiert in Sevilla gegen Spanien die höchste Niederlage seit 1931 und verpasst somit die Finalrunde der Nations League. Während die DFB-Truppe sich historisch schwach präsentierte, führten die starken Spanier bereits zur Pause mit 3:0. Noch nie zuvor lag man unter Bundestrainer Jogi Löw nach den ersten 45 Minuten so deutlich zurück. Für die dominierenden Spanier trafen Alvaro Morata (17. Minute), Ferran Torres (33.), Rodri (38.) und in der zweiten Hälfte erneut der überragende Torres (55., 74.). Für den 6:0-Endstand sorgte Joker Mikel Oyarzabal. Spanien erreicht damit hochverdient das Finalturnier, was 2021 ausgetragen wird.

snippet.description:
Die Deutsche Nationalmannschaft liegt am Boden: Das 0:6 in Spanien ist die höchste Niederlage seit fast 90 Jahren. Lasst uns auf die aktuellen Probleme blicken, was macht "Die Mannschaft" des DFB falsch? Über Bundestrainer Jogi Löw müssen wir reden... er wirkte völlig hilflos und wusste nicht, was er tun soll. Abseits dieser Personalie, laufen jedoch im DFB-Team weitere Dinge schief: Wo sind die Führungsspieler? Wer gibt auf dem Platz Anweisungen? Dazu fehlt insbesondere in der Defensive die Qualität auf Weltklasse-Niveau, um gegen Top-Teams bestehen zu könenn. Die System-Frage kann man hier auch stellen... benötigt man wirklich 2 Formationen, um bei der EM 2021 Erfolg zu haben? Die Deutsche Nationalmannschaft liegt am Boden, das ist ein Fakt. Ist Jogi Löw noch der richtige Mann? Die Kritik wird auf jeden Fall immer lauter. 

#DFB #Löw #Nationalmannschaft
----

snippet.title: Können wir den Klimawandel ohne Atomenergie stoppen?
snippet.description:
Quellen: https://sites.google.com/view/sources-climate-nuclear/

In den letzten Jahren behaupten immer mehr Stimmen aus der Wissenschaft und dem Umweltschutz dass wir den Klimawandel nur mit Hilfe von Atomenergie bremsen können. Dass die Klimakatastrophe ohne Atomenergie sogar überhaupt nicht mehr verhindert werden kann. Das schockierte vor allem die, die schon seit Jahrzehnten gegen Atomenergie ankämpfen - und sich langsam gewinnen sahen. Was hat es damit also auf sich?

Soundcloud: http://bit.ly/2n8dAE5
Facebook: http://bit.ly/2n6AUBX
Twitter: http://bit.ly/2DDeT83
Instagram: http://bit.ly/2DEN7r3

Dinge erklärt – Kurzgesagt ist ein Wissenschaftskanal der komplexe Themen aus Weltraumforschung, Physik, Biologie, Politik, Philosophie und Technik einfach und verständlich in animierter Form erklärt.

Impressum: https://go.funk.net/impressum

Wir veröffentlichen alle zwei Wochen ein neues Video auf deutsch. Mal Übersetzungen von unserem englischsprachigen Kanal, mal exklusive Inhalte für den deutschen Markt.

Seit dem 28.09.2017 ist Dinge Erklärt – Kurzgesagt ein Angebot von funk

snippet.title: Minecraft Survivalist VS 3 Hitmen
snippet.description:
Minecraft Survivalist VS 3 Hitmen. This might even be more INSANE than manhunt.
Merch: https://www.dream.shop

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Patreon (Plugin): https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

BadBoyHalo: @BadBoyHalo 
George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Hitmen. This video there are THREE hunters/hitmen instead of just one.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.16 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to survive for 60 minutes, while my friend George AND my friend Sapnap AND my friend BadBoyHalo tries to prevent me from surviving. They can see me through walls, and the world is small. It's a chase, a race, and it's super intense. A lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

If this video gets 1,500,000 likes we'll do it again!

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed runner / survivalist in Minecraft against a killer / assassin / hitmen

snippet.title: here are some things i thrifted in nyc :)
snippet.description:
instagram  ➭ https://www.instagram.com/best.dressed/
subscribe for more vids ➭ http://bit.ly/bestdressedfam
✨ the jewelry i designed ➭ https://enroutejewelry.com/collections/bestdressed
shop my presets ➭ https://www.bestdressedstore.com
my second channel ➭ http://bit.ly/bestmess
twitter ➭ @bestdressed
tik tok lol ➭ @bestdressed


Come thrifting with me in NYC! In this video, I give you a tour of my favorite thrift stores in Manhattan and Brooklyn, try on all the thrifted dresses, jackets, sweaters, jeans, and t-shirts I’ve accumulated over the past couple months, and demonstrate my hidden talent of stuffing a truly obscene amount of fabric into my pants. Also thank you for your patience with my upload schedule during the past month! I tried to film this thrift haul a couple weeks ago on election day and the vibes were just ~weird~ because I was so nervous, so I decided to scrap the entire thing, and then there’s been a ton of construction in my building so it’s been infuriatingly hard to find a time quiet enough to film. Anyhow an entire month later, here she is!


✰ WHAT I’M WEARING ✰
safety pin earrings: i designed them! (https://enroutejewelry.com/products/safetypin-earrings)
pearl headband: jenn im x 8 other reasons (sold out, similar: https://amzn.to/3kQD58m)
fuzzy coat: marc jacobs (https://bit.ly/2Hffn7x)
tan pants: & other stories (similar: https://bit.ly/3fjqf0D)
green corduroy pants: rollas (https://bit.ly/2IRHudJ)
polka dot top: majorelle (https://bit.ly/35GmkXo)
high waisted jeans: levi’s (https://bit.ly/2Kn10z9)


✰ THRIFT STORES I MENTIONED ✰

L Train Vintage - Bushwick
106 Knickerbocker Ave, Brooklyn, NY 11237

Urban Jungle - Bushwick
118 Knickerbocker Ave, Brooklyn, NY 11237

L Train Vintage - East Village
204 1st Ave, New York, NY 10009

Goodwill - Union Square
7 W 14th St, New York, NY 10011


♫ MUSIC ♫
danish girl my marlin’s dreaming (https://marlinsdreaming.bandcamp.com/album/lizard-tears)
charlie brown’s day off by louie zong (https://louiezong.bandcamp.com/track/charlie-browns-day-off)
ballroom music from epidemic sound (http://bit.ly/2VW00n4)


✰ FAQ ✰
what’s your name? ashley
what’s your instagram? @best.dressed
how old are you? 22 (born in 1998)
how tall are you? 5'5"
what’s your ethnicity? half british and half burmese
what equipment do you use to film?
 ➭  main camera: panasonic lumix gh5s (https://amzn.to/2Nb0W1z)
 ➭  8-18 mm lens (https://amzn.to/3bmVoxd)
 ➭  12-35mm lens (https://amzn.to/2JiSrz7)
 ➭  on camera mic: rode videomic pro+ (https://amzn.to/2QHfZBU)
 ➭  voiceover mic: blue yeti usb mic (https://go.magik.ly/ml/yshp/)
 ➭  vlog camera: canon g7x mark ii (http://amzn.to/2DfL4cZ)
 ➭  canon m50 (https://amzn.to/2Dp1bnk)
 ➭  editing: final cut pro
